                <span class="text-xs font-black text-springer-yellow uppercase tracking-widest">Introduction</span>
                <h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mt-2 mb-6 uppercase tracking-tighter leading-none">Numerical Methods Approach</h1>
                <div class="h-1.5 w-32 springer-yellow mb-8"></div>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl">
                    As highlighted in the book, "numerical analysis is the study of algorithms that use numerical approximation for the problems of mathematical analysis." In environmental sciences, where models are often too complex for analytical solutions, these methods become the primary tool to understand climate stability and ecological shifts.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
